metadata.name: Dice Legacy
metadata.description: Dice Legacy is a compilation of various characters, items, and buildings from the Dice City saga. Embark on an unforgettable journey through Dice City, where chance, destiny, and the power of dice intertwine. Join Kabi, Lorenzo, and Otto as they uncover their extraordinary abilities, navigate the realms of gods and mortals to confront the malevolent forces threatening the fate of their beloved city.
